snippet.textDisplay: Happy birthday clash Royale! I was wondering if I could get in touch with a clash Royale team member so I can pitch some ideas. One of those ideas being a 2v2 ladder. This would be something new that many people could look forward to. Instead of always just pushing trophies on 1v1 ladder they could push on 2v2 with a friend, family member etc. creating new excitement within the game. Within the community this could open up a whole new stream of meta decks and different combos within 2v2. Ultimately bringing new players in and keeping current players for good. Any feedback from anybody would be much appreciated!
